commit.message:
dwarf2cfi: Flush queued saves at the end of the prologue.

There's little point at holding onto these saves indefinitely.

PR bootstrap/49680
        * dwarf2cfi.c (create_cfi_notes): Flush queued saves at the
        end of the prologue.

From-SVN: r176066
